::Spears::

She pulled her hand back through the hole and looked down,"I cannot 
let you free.  I am under orders. I cannot." She looked back through 
the hole at Striker. She whispered, "I'm sorry." She took a deep 
breath, "I am Master Prebon's now. I have to obey his orders."  She 
wanted to finish with, no matter how much it's killing me inside to 
do so, but she couldn't say the words.
